            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Adding on to what Blckknght said, a decorator doesn&apos;t just return something else, it can return any object.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
